    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="ko">
    <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8">
      <title>페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</title>
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
      <style>
        body {
          font-family: sans-serif;
          background: #f9f9f9;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          height: 100vh;
          margin: 0;
          text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2em;
          color: #333;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
          color: #666;
          font-size: 1.1em;
          margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        button {
          display: inline-block;
          background: #4e73df;
          color: white;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
        }

        button:hover {
          background: #2c5de5;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <h1 style="font-size: 3em; color: #2c5de5;">429</h1> 
      <h1>⏳ 잠시만요!</h1>
      <p>요청이 너무 많아요. 서버가 잠시 숨을 고르는 중이에요. 잠시 후 다시 시도해 주세요.</p>
      <button id="gobutton" onclick="location.href='/'" disabled>5초 후에 버튼이 활성화돼요...</button>
    </body>
    <script>
      // 5초 후에 버튼 활성화
    let seconds = 5;
    const countdownEl = document.getElementById("gobutton");

    const timer = setInterval(() => {
    seconds--;
    countdownEl.textContent = `${seconds}초 후에 버튼이 활성화돼요...`;

    if (seconds === 0) {
        clearInterval(timer);
        document.getElementById("gobutton").disabled = false;
        countdownEl.textContent = "홈으로 돌아가기";
    }
    }, 1000);

    </script>
    </html>